    {
      "id": "699a02a8-f5c9-40af-bfed-b0f6b8ea0fcd",
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "source": "1. Tree traversals  \r\n- Depth-first search (DFS)  \r\n    + Preorder: visit, left, right  \r\n        eg. D (BAC) (FEG)\r\n    + Inorder: left, visit, right  \r\n        eg. (ABC) D (EFG)\r\n    + Postorder: left, right, visit  \r\n        eg. (ACB) (EGF) D\r\n\r\n- Breadth-first search (BFS)  \r\n    eg. D (BF) (ACEG)\r\n\r\n2. Depth of a node  \r\n=length or distance from the root\r\n",
      "metadata": {
        "language": "markdown",
        "id": "699a02a8-f5c9-40af-bfed-b0f6b8ea0fcd"
      }
    },
